{"tid":550223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"為左做呢套視覺小說，我地唱作左兩首歌","createTime":"2018-02-04T14:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T16:46:25.000Z","uid":164179,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00d2ec227eb23bdc4846667875e8d2339754ec14","tid":550223,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222347_31ea311c5103fd259bbcf83174f59527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222347_31ea311c5103fd259bbcf83174f59527.jpg&h=998605ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先，套視覺小說叫《Free-lancer》 <br />\nFb：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2F&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a0be26bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/</a> <br />\n<br />\n成個故事已經正式發佈，由社畜+自由身artist組隊完成既作品 <br />\n<br />\n之前每日被工作壓搾，一直做唔到想做既事 <br />\n外人睇你唔起、無錢買樓、女都走埋，又唔想咁樣on99一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到一日，終於的起心肝，想做一套屬於自己既作品，講一個令香港人有共鳴既故事 <br />\n<br />\n我地心目中想要既作品，一定要有主題曲 <br />\n而故事其中一個角色係歌手，無理由連一首佢唱既歌都無 <br />\n所以就算資源緊絀，我地都堅持唱作左呢兩首歌 <br />\n一首好認真，一首搞gag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家聽下，如果鍾意既、有興趣既，再睇睇我地套作品 <br />\n感受一下我地團隊呢半年既努力 <br />\n<br />\n唔講太多，聽歌啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主題曲《飛翔》 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/videos/1200568546741896/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2Fvideos%2F1200568546741896%2F%20&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=78d62b4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/videos/1200568546741896/ </a><br />\n唔想上facebook可以去youtube <br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/sdezMk34vh8 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsdezMk34vh8%20&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a28d1cb5\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/sdezMk34vh8 </a><br />\n<br />\n作曲：Ling <br />\n編曲：Ling <br />\n作詞：雨田明 <br />\n主唱：Aoi <br />\n　 <br />\n孤雛飛鳥　傷重躺於一方 <br />\n劇痛難抹消　亦滿心悲愴 <br />\n沒再求看天　收起這一雙翅　最怕錯誤再多 <br />\n　 <br />\n卻步怕幻覺　自困這身束縛　已忘記雲那端　另有光 <br />\n停望鏡像　剩這軀殼　So why don&rsquo;t you spread the wings？ <br />\n　 <br />\nFly away　Fly away　劃破這愁雲尋天地 <br />\nNever stay　Never stay　暴雨灑去傷悲 <br />\nFly away　Fly away　淚眼抬頭仍難看星 <br />\n翼未痛　心不碎　便再次　展翅高飛 <br />\n　 <br />\n孤身飛去　海角遠飛一遍 <br />\n浴血和嘆息　夢裡早不見 <br />\n若仰頭看天　黑影會終消去　與你再遇並肩 <br />\n　 <br />\n錯誤裡自覺　突破這身束縛　暗夜裡月有星　亦有光 <br />\n忘掉往日　幻痛消退　So let&rsquo;s go, take to the sky <br />\n　 <br />\nFly away　Fly away　劃破這愁雲尋天地 <br />\nNever stay　Never stay　暴雨灑去傷悲 <br />\nFly away　Fly away　淚眼抬頭仍難看星 <br />\n翼未痛　心不碎　定再次　展翅高飛 <br />\n　 <br />\nRace the wind　Free my heart <br />\n看盡各地晚空　月與星 <br />\n無限旅途　任我飛去　So freedom is by my side <br />\n　 <br />\nOn my way　On my way　別錯過看透這天地 <br />\nNever stay　Never stay　未怕冰霰紛霏 <br />\nFly away　Fly away　掠過雷雲翱翔破風 <br />\n逐夢去　終不退　定永要　展翅高飛 <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; <br />\n<br />\n另一首，係個故事入面一個女角既角色歌 <br />\n如果可以明晒歌詞所有梗，sorry，你同填詞果個一樣都幾毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《熾熱心跳Sing and Love》 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/videos/1201702793295138/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2Fvideos%2F1201702793295138%2F%20&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e0181fcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/videos/1201702793295138/ </a><br />\nyoutube版： <br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/a0szzfnG7iw \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa0szzfnG7iw%20&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a8fe83d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/a0szzfnG7iw </a><br />\n<br />\n作曲：Ling <br />\n編曲：Ling <br />\n作詞：雨田明 <br />\n原唱：楊羽媛 <br />\n主唱：Aoi <br />\n　 <br />\n腦細叫我咪走住　要撐到清晨 <br />\n但冇瞓我邊有靈魂　so me覆佢　おやすみなさい <br />\n放假再去轉Tokyo　吃貨最開心 <br />\n吃足一季 再拿來手掣　雷狼龍我亂砌 <br />\n　 <br />\n高富帥博士沒意思　I just know 敵将 is Doctor Lee <br />\n最掂哪個oppa唔太知 <br />\n要戀愛　期待佢　教我破DarkSoul　齊瞓晏覺再食滯 <br />\n　 <br />\n伴我玩　再任食　即使踢拖　也都不錯 <br />\n吃炸饅頭　油麵切雞拌叉燒　便開心得唱歌 <br />\n若要阻　我玩樂　錢銀再多　ダメでしょう <br />\n我是自由　隨著意走心至跳　Let&rsquo;s feel heart beat　Sing and Love <br />\n　 <br />\n腦細叫我咪走住　要教佢英文 <br />\n但見佢我經已頭暈　 so me覆佢　I go to school by bus <br />\n放假我要變Master　最愛FGO <br />\n首抽好正　卻無人可曬　窮宅毒要大嗌 <br />\n　 <br />\n高富帥博士沒意思　I just know 敵将 is Doctor Lee <br />\n最掂哪個oppa唔太知 <br />\n要戀愛　期待佢　教我破DarkSoul　齊瞓晏覺再食滯 <br />\n　 <br />\n伴我玩　再任食　即使踢拖　也都不錯 <br />\n著住條裙　蒙面擸刀扮2B　便開心得唱歌 <br />\n若要阻　我玩樂　錢銀再多　ダメでしょう <br />\n我是自由　隨著意走心至跳　Let&rsquo;s feel heart beat　Sing and Love <br />\n　 <br />\n（是你麼&hellip;&hellip;er，窮鬼？）　但仍想一起過 <br />\n最掂那個oppa唔要囉 <br />\n要戀愛　期待你　與我看one piece　齊吃到夠也未滯 <br />\n　 <br />\n伴你走　再玩樂　少錢課金　也都不錯 <br />\n搏命十連　全沒五星遊非洲　亦開心得唱歌 <br />\n食瞓玩　冇寂寞　一起踢拖　いきましょう <br />\n快樂自由　隨著你走心至跳　Let&rsquo;s feel heart beat　Sing and Love"},{"pid":"754a324fd1b141820bbe87d1df64447d782fb5ee","tid":550223,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fd9207f8c7ce3884368ea5023f9d193c190558d","tid":550223,"uid":164179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"聽完歌，懇請大家睇埋個故事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地用呢個故事去參加左個比賽，希望得到實際嘅認同 <br />\n就算撇除個比賽，我地都想多D人睇到個作品，始終呢個係專為香港人寫嘅故事 <br />\n<br />\n【故事簡介】 <br />\n這是一個無法離開手機的年代。無論吃飯、乘車、購物、供樓、搭艇洗頭、叫家鄉雞和修改會議規則，都能用手機完成。 <br />\n<br />\n而在這個與香港極度相似的城市，任何人想找Freelancer幫忙，抑或Freelancer想接工作，都能用「EC Freelance」這個App做到。人人輕鬆透過手機發委託或賺外快，手機，變得更加不可或缺。 <br />\n<br />\n阿堂是這城市的一個小市民，以全職Freelancer為本業。一天，他意外拾到一部發紅光的奇怪手機。同時，市內暗地發生著不同的罪案，這些罪案發生時，現場都閃現了異樣的紅光&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n一如以往的日常，意想不到的衝擊。隨著一個陰謀擴散蔓延，阿堂亦漸漸捲入事件的洪流之中&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n命運，從此徹底改寫。 <br />\n<br />\n【截圖】 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222815_fe07eee1f0268775c646e844b05bff2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222815_fe07eee1f0268775c646e844b05bff2d.png&h=d0a3c3b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222827_d9b6f4554ead74cebd62effb6a671a52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222827_d9b6f4554ead74cebd62effb6a671a52.png&h=4abe1281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222839_5f3b980f0213c331c10559468a556d31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222839_5f3b980f0213c331c10559468a556d31.png&h=b9f719e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222849_afc8e8f20f2d9785d7bcd30c11fbfe51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222849_afc8e8f20f2d9785d7bcd30c11fbfe51.png&h=b230b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【點樣睇】 <br />\n<br />\n個故事喺一個叫oice既app度發佈，所以要dl咗個app至睇得，免費，放心 <br />\n<br />\nAN： <br />\n<a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.oice&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3c372780\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oice</a> <br />\nIOS： <br />\n<a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/oice/id1248232355?ls=1&amp;mt=8 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Foice%2Fid1248232355%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8%20&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e726f934\" target=\"_blank\">http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/oice/id1248232355?ls=1&amp;mt=8 </a><br />\n<br />\ndl完之後，就可以點呢條link睇： <br />\n<a href=\"http://oice.app.link/free_lancer \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foice.app.link%2Ffree_lancer%20&d=gyvbeEVwMHfqlcoh%2F4gC2aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=90c3e285\" target=\"_blank\">http://oice.app.link/free_lancer </a><br />\n（用電腦開呢條link可以試睇第一話第一節，但之後都係要用app睇） <br />\n<br />\n唔鍾意開上面條link，可以直接入app，點畫面上面個filter <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222922_6d9c78e96a9f24462c15794db02bd145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222922_6d9c78e96a9f24462c15794db02bd145.jpg&h=533e9f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀「奇幻/科幻」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222930_e22da9ff7586620e683da3dcef6a2ea9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222930_e22da9ff7586620e683da3dcef6a2ea9.jpg&h=f854c543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就會見到我地套作品《Free-lancer》 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222943_5fbfa7b00f3117c39df95f00e9165d9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222943_5fbfa7b00f3117c39df95f00e9165d9a.jpg&h=24ac8b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【FAQ】 <br />\n<br />\nQ：dl app之後係英文/日文介面，搵唔到你個故仔 <br />\nA：轉返中文介面就會見到，入app，點左下角個圈圈，可以轉做中文 <br />\n<br />\nQ：點解個故仔有《光輝歲用》同《小林正雪》嘅角色？係咪抄襲？ <br />\nA：呢個故事用oice平台製作，除左自家製嘅原創角色，亦有用到oice素材庫嘅人物，全部都由原作者親自upload，已得到同意使用。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：點解睇咗幾話之後，個app要我畀錢先可以繼續睇？ <br />\nA：等一段時間就可以繼續免費睇，一開始係兩個鐘，有段時間係推廣期等5分鐘就得。 <br />\n<br />\nQ：睇咗，想支持你地。 <br />\nA：多謝！懇請大家、跪求大家，如果想支持我地，請入我地個故事，點一點畫面左邊個心心 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/223004_f47b82cda52577506c125431b67fee9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F223004_f47b82cda52577506c125431b67fee9c.png&h=98aa562b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有呢個心心數夠多，oice平台同比賽主辦方先會知道我地係人氣作品，我地先有動力繼續做落去 <br />\n另外，都請大家like一like我地fb，關注我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nQ：點咗個心心，佢話未能讚好喎 <br />\nA：係官方嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等一陣再點過，總會成功 <br />\n<br />\nQ：睇咗，垃撚圾，收皮啦。 <br />\nA：多謝，請畀D意見我地，我地一定會努力改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a31e15d7fd848e2dc6272c78eb5072bc55d175c","tid":550223,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"又你呢個平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4692abb6ef9436684951eb115fe4c401e7d17fae","tid":550223,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"754a324fd1b141820bbe87d1df64447d782fb5ee","tid":550223,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"為咗做呢套視覺小說，我地唱作咗兩首歌<br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以後唔敢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e212428d95e81c9b4c8380af8f1f1b0f43fe9fb","tid":550223,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a31e15d7fd848e2dc6272c78eb5072bc55d175c","tid":550223,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"又你呢個平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"巴打成日見到個平台？ <br />\n我反而覺得冇乜人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3789482659950b5fa9d30b35f167c16a74caefc","tid":550223,"uid":164179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T17:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f